Actually AE groups aren't the issue with this change.  Scintilation never hit our pets.  It's rain spells like Sirocco that would hit the pet for one wave while hopefully hitting the MOB for three.  If anyone uses a Rain spell in an AE group they need to have their head examined.  Sirocco is a Mages most mana efficient damage spell if at least two waves hit for full.  It's one that I regularly keep memed and am quite happy that my pet no longer eats a wave.<br>
